in the system to make every CTP data packet send with low power listening
enabled:

  event void SendNotifier.aboutToSend[AM_COLLECTION_DATA](uint8_t dest,
      message_t *msg) {
    call LowPowerListening.setRxSleepInterval(msg, 512);
  }

